Idiosyncratic Adverse Reaction Type

https://healthterminologies.gov.au/fhir/ValueSet/idiosyncratic-adverse-reaction-type-1

The Idiosyncratic Adverse Reaction Type value set includes values that represent adverse reaction types that are intrinsic to an individual.
